! Namespace ŌĆö settings & diagnostics

!! Feature flags

Each feature is off by default. Toggle to enable.

<$checkbox tiddler="$:/config/rimir/namespace/walk-up" field="text" checked="yes" unchecked="no" default="no"> ''Walk-up'' ŌĆö resolve bare refs by climbing the source tiddler's path segments</$checkbox>

<$checkbox tiddler="$:/config/rimir/namespace/implicit-context" field="text" checked="yes" unchecked="no" default="no"> ''Implicit context'' ŌĆö derive context from the `context` field on tiddlers</$checkbox>

<$checkbox tiddler="$:/config/rimir/namespace/pseudo-expansion" field="text" checked="yes" unchecked="no" default="no"> ''Pseudo expansion'' ŌĆö enable `_latest` and other pseudo-segment modules</$checkbox>

<$checkbox tiddler="$:/config/rimir/namespace/aliases" field="text" checked="yes" unchecked="no" default="no"> ''Aliases'' ŌĆö enable exact and pattern alias resolution</$checkbox>

