!! Diagnostic filters

These operators are exposed for scripting / debugging:

* `[<ref>ns-resolve<source>]` ŌĆö resolve a single ref as if from `<source>`
* `[<ref>ns-resolve-class<source>]` ŌĆö CSS class (`ns-resolved` / `ns-unresolved`)
* `[<title>ns-backlinks[]]` ŌĆö sources that reference `<title>`
* `[<title>ns-forwardlinks[]]` ŌĆö targets `<title>` references

Tiddler info sidebar includes a ''NS Backlinks'' tab showing the reverse
index for the current tiddler.
